{"tid":1612476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多區開花最大缺點","createTime":"2019-10-02T09:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:00:33.000Z","uid":135398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e84b3a363a3378b8122c0742ee7dcb1f7764a96","tid":1612476,"uid":135398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係即時資訊根本跟唔切</span><br />\n多區搞的確令警犬部署上更加困難，但當太多突發、手足快閃嘅出現，即使係同一區嘅手足都完全唔清楚唔了解其他位置發生緊咩事，<span style=\"color: red;\">更重要係唔知其他位置仲有冇手足</span>。<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(琴日黃大仙發夢就有過百人，因爲有手足誤報龍翔道比狗清場後冇晒手足，而轉場九龍城但最後乜都冇做到)</span><br />\n<br />\n而琴日更加疲於奔命嘅係一眾記者朋友，有好多地方同狗衝突緊而附近係冇記者朋友在場拍到。要記得呢場運動記者嘅鏡頭係我地好重要嘅文宣力量，如果冇記者在場記錄黑警嘅暴行，係我地好大損失。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願中槍手足一切安好</span>"},{"pid":"e5447d93484f8dd524a965b38247614860890b12","tid":1612476,"uid":135398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"同意繼續多區搞，但要繼續改善問題，唔忍心咁多手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cc6a50f1bd4ee876bf3021df4a298a333b5c07","tid":1612476,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊地區戰要解決哨兵不足既問題<br />\n升級哨兵系統，要納入街坊做哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1612385/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1612385/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2f1a7c437016a47e898351220106841f4eda9850","tid":1612476,"uid":135398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6cc6a50f1bd4ee876bf3021df4a298a333b5c07","tid":1612476,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊地區戰要解決哨兵不足既問題<br />\n升級哨兵系統，要納入街坊做哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1612385/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1612385/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":